{"tid":1400154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"莫乃光同另外五位議員去信3M施壓要求保障市民！","createTime":"2019-08-03T11:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T11:54:03.000Z","uid":41058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab877f1b4a6ccc839d304fe68f173b4fae2e954","tid":1400154,"uid":41058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/191313141299862/posts/725397174558120?s=707396460&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F191313141299862%2Fposts%2F725397174558120%3Fs%3D707396460%26sfns%3Dmo&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=053683c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/191313141299862/posts/725397174558120?s=707396460&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n#莫乃光：不久前有網民向我表示關注警察被指向3M公司及其分銷商查取其貼紙產品銷售資料，顯然針對各區連儂牆及其參與者，我和專業議政的議員們一起向3M香港公司書面查詢，並要求他們不應在沒有足夠法律理據(例如法庭搜查令)下向警方提供資料。我們將繼續關注3M公司的回應，希望他們能夠繼續為香港人提供我們表達自由的支援和方便。<br />\n<br />\nDennis Kwok 郭榮鏗 Kenneth Leung 梁繼昌 Ip Kin Yuen 葉建源 Joseph Lee 李國麟 邵家臻 Charles Mok 莫乃光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6bCewra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6bCewra.png&h=a567563c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHq0rZx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHq0rZx.png&h=709b0db2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6d56c1b360e26a3fdabd9c2f630376308aa3698","tid":1400154,"uid":41058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:31:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be8854308266d03c9c1b67f61e1ca4d71a394414","tid":1400154,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"154d68aee8cdb9480886db15fd1dd58f95eb06e9","tid":1400154,"uid":41058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"}]}